description:
This is a 32 minute workout called 'HIIT Workout - Insane 30 Minute Treadmill Workout' from the channel AbundantYou with Dr Kevin.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Cardio/Treadmill.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Looking for a HIIT workout on the treadmill TO BURN SOME FAT!? Try this Insane 30 Minute Treadmill Workout with Dr. Kevin Sarich, DC. #HIIT #HIITWorkout #Treadmill

Running on the treadmill can be easier than running outdoors, for a variety of good reasons. Treadmills give you complete control, enabling you to adjust the speed, incline, warm-up period, cool-down period, and amount of energy you expend. 

I recommend you try this 30 minute treadmill workout to take your fitness to the next level!

I will be your own personal fitness instructor, motivating you to the very end of the treadmill workout!

HIIT workouts - known as High Intensity Interval Training, are the most effective way to burn fat in the shortest amount of time possible. However, most people don't utilize this type of workout enough. 

It's recommend to perform a 10-30 minute HIIT workout 2-3 times a week, with 24 hour rest in between HIIT workouts, in addition to other variety of fitness activities.
